STEP 3: Replace Files in Order

3.1 Replace app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml

Copy the complete AndroidManifest code I provided earlier.

3.2 Update app/build.gradle (Module: app)

```gradle
android {
    compileSdk 34

    defaultConfig {
        applicationId "com.niraven.app"
        minSdk 21
        targetSdk 34
        versionCode 1
        versionName "1.0"
    }

    buildTypes {
        release {
            minifyEnabled false
            proguardFiles getDefaultProguardFile('proguard-android-optimize.txt'), 'proguard-rules.pro'
        }
    }
    
    compileOptions {
        sourceCompatibility JavaVersion.VERSION_1_8
        targetCompatibility JavaVersion.VERSION_1_8
    }
}

dependencies {
    implementation 'androidx.appcompat:appcompat:1.6.1'
    implementation 'com.google.android.material:material:1.9.0'
    implementation 'androidx.constraintlayout:constraintlayout:2.1.4'
}
```

3.3 Create Java Files

Create each Java file in the correct package and copy-paste the code:

1. NiravenApp.java
2. LoginActivity.java
3. MainDashboardActivity.java
4. ChatAnalyzerActivity.java
5. BluetoothChatActivity.java

3.4 Create Layout Files

Create each XML layout file in res/layout/:

1. activity_login.xml
2. activity_dashboard.xml
3. activity_chat_analyzer.xml
4. activity_bluetooth_chat.xml

STEP 4: Layout Files Content

4.1 activity_login.xml

```xml
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<LinearLayout xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android"
    android:layout_width="match_parent"
    android:layout_height="match_parent"
    android:orientation="vertical"
    android:padding="24dp"
    android:gravity="center"
    android:background="#f5f5f5">

    <TextView
        android:id="@+id/tvAppName"
        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
        android:text="NIRAVEN"
        android:textSize="32sp"
        android:textStyle="bold"
        android:textColor="#2196F3"
        android:layout_marginBottom="40dp" />

    <EditText
        android:id="@+id/etUsername"
        android:layout_width="match_parent"
        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
        android:hint="Username"
        android:padding="16dp"
        android:background="@drawable/edittext_background"
        android:layout_marginBottom="16dp" />

    <EditText
        android:id="@+id/etPassword"
        android:layout_width="match_parent"
        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
        android:hint="Password"
        android:inputType="textPassword"
        android:padding="16dp"
        android:background="@drawable/edittext_background"
        android:layout_marginBottom="24dp" />

    <Button
        android:id="@+id/btnLogin"
        android:layout_width="match_parent"
        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
        android:text="Login"
        android:textSize="16sp"
        android:padding="16dp"
        android:background="#2196F3"
        android:textColor="#FFFFFF"
        android:layout_marginBottom="8dp" />

    <Button
        android:id="@+id/btnRegister"
        android:layout_width="match_parent"
        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
        android:text="Register"
        android:textSize="16sp"
        android:padding="16dp"
        android:background="#4CAF50"
        android:textColor="#FFFFFF" />

</LinearLayout>
```

4.2 Create res/drawable/edittext_background.xml

```xml
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<shape xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android">
    <solid android:color="#FFFFFF" />
    <stroke android:width="1dp" android:color="#E0E0E0" />
    <corners android:radius="8dp" />
</shape>
```

