STEP 5: Build and Run

5.1 Sync Project

```bash
# After adding all files, click "Sync Now" in Android Studio
# Fix any import errors or missing dependencies
```

5.2 Connect Android Device

```bash
1. Enable Developer Options on your Android phone
   - Go to Settings â†’ About Phone â†’ Tap "Build Number" 7 times
2. Enable USB Debugging in Developer Options
3. Connect phone to computer via USB cable
```

5.3 Run the App

```bash
1. In Android Studio, click the green "Run" button
2. Select your connected device
3. Wait for installation
4. App will launch on your phone!
```

